00:00:47.570 --> 00:00:51.280 align:middle line:84%
And so these stories
enable us to remember

00:00:51.280 --> 00:00:54.750 align:middle line:90%
who we fundamentally are.

00:00:54.750 --> 00:00:58.805 align:middle line:84%
This isn't a classic historical
romance, the way we think

00:00:58.805 --> 00:00:59.605 align:middle line:90%
