00:01:36.910 --> 00:01:38.110 align:middle line:90%
read the series of books.

00:01:38.110 --> 00:01:40.630 align:middle line:90%
It is so juicy and tempting.

00:01:40.630 --> 00:01:42.192 align:middle line:90%
So welcome back, Gates.

00:01:42.192 --> 00:01:43.150 align:middle line:90%
>> MCKIBBIN: Thank you.

00:01:43.150 --> 00:01:46.878 align:middle line:10%
It's so good to be back and
talking about love this time.

00:01:46.878 --> 00:01:47.920 align:middle line:10%
>> REGINA: You know what?

00:01:47.920 --> 00:01:48.720 align:middle line:90%
It's true.

00:01:48.720 --> 00:01:51.370 align:middle line:84%
What the world needs
now is love, sweet love.

00:01:51.370 --> 00:01:54.550 align:middle line:84%
Man, there couldn't be
a more perfect topic

00:01:54.550 --> 00:01:55.970 align:middle line:90%
for the times than love.

00:01:55.970 --> 00:01:59.710 align:middle line:84%
So first of all, here you're
talking to dead presidents

00:01:59.710 --> 00:02:01.900 align:middle line:84%
and now, this is a
whole different thing

00:02:01.900 --> 00:02:04.330 align:middle line:90%
that happened back then, right?

00:02:04.330 --> 00:02:06.820 align:middle line:84%
Wasn't this from,
maybe, 20 years

00:02:06.820 --> 00:02:08.170 align:middle line:90%
ago when this first started?

00:02:08.170 --> 00:02:13.420 align:middle line:84%
>> MCKIBBIN: About 20 years ago,
I get guidance from spirit that

00:02:13.420 --> 00:02:14.410 align:middle line:90%
is very simple.

00:02:14.410 --> 00:02:16.830 align:middle line:84%
Grab a journal, grab a
pen, let's get started.

00:02:16.830 --> 00:02:19.330 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: And then you just--
you're sitting here like this

00:02:19.330 --> 00:02:20.455 align:middle line:90%
and your hand's doing this.

00:02:20.455 --> 00:02:23.590 align:middle line:84%
>> MCKIBBIN: And I never know
what the topic is going to be.

00:02:23.590 --> 00:02:28.180 align:middle line:10%
So I started writing the first
book, it was about Atlantis.

00:02:28.180 --> 00:02:31.870 align:middle line:84%
And I thought, wow,
this is different.

00:02:31.870 --> 00:02:34.660 align:middle line:10%
I wonder if it's real, I
wonder if it's authentic,

00:02:34.660 --> 00:02:36.655 align:middle line:10%
I wonder if they're
making this up.

00:02:36.655 --> 00:02:39.730 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: That's important
because you personally

00:02:39.730 --> 00:02:41.492 align:middle line:84%
didn't know anything
about Atlantis.

00:02:41.492 --> 00:02:43.075 align:middle line:84%
I mean, that's not
in your wheelhouse.

00:02:43.075 --> 00:02:43.765 align:middle line:90%
>> MCKIBBIN: No.

00:02:43.765 --> 00:02:44.020 align:middle line:90%
It's not.

00:02:44.020 --> 00:02:46.395 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: Now, first people
need to know you were a very

00:02:46.395 --> 00:02:47.855 align:middle line:90%
high-powered businesswoman, OK?

00:02:47.855 --> 00:02:48.655 align:middle line:90%
>> MCKIBBIN: Yes.

00:02:48.655 --> 00:02:50.950 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: You were a very
successful high powered

00:02:50.950 --> 00:02:54.370 align:middle line:84%
businesswoman and you got--
you became ill at one point,

00:02:54.370 --> 00:02:57.100 align:middle line:84%
something happened, cracked
open the old egg here up

00:02:57.100 --> 00:03:00.170 align:middle line:84%
to the universe, and things
started pouring through you.

00:03:00.170 --> 00:03:02.800 align:middle line:84%
So just to get that
background out of the way,

00:03:02.800 --> 00:03:07.790 align:middle line:84%
you were not studying
esoterica like this at all.

00:03:07.790 --> 00:03:10.000 align:middle line:90%
So let's now go from there.

00:03:10.000 --> 00:03:13.720 align:middle line:84%
>> MCKIBBIN: Wasn't studying
anything about Atlantis.

00:03:13.720 --> 00:03:16.270 align:middle line:90%
I had never read about Atlantis.

00:03:16.270 --> 00:03:20.230 align:middle line:84%
Suddenly, I'm sitting
writing about what

00:03:20.230 --> 00:03:24.640 align:middle line:84%
I think is a fantasy, a fiction,
something that may or may not

00:03:24.640 --> 00:03:26.470 align:middle line:90%
have existed.

00:03:26.470 --> 00:03:33.100 align:middle line:84%
And a couple who come together
after an androgynous person,

00:03:33.100 --> 00:03:38.350 align:middle line:84%
makes the choice of going
through a high frequency

00:03:38.350 --> 00:03:42.850 align:middle line:84%
spiritual process and
being split into two.

00:03:42.850 --> 00:03:46.730 align:middle line:84%
Into identical twins--
a male and a female.

00:03:46.730 --> 00:03:51.130 align:middle line:84%
So I'm writing all of this
thinking, this is phenomenal.

00:03:51.130 --> 00:03:52.580 align:middle line:90%
How can it be real?

00:03:52.580 --> 00:03:53.770 align:middle line:90%
How can it be true?

00:03:53.770 --> 00:03:57.550 align:middle line:84%
But I keep going and I
get deeper and deeper

00:03:57.550 --> 00:03:58.810 align:middle line:90%
into the story.

00:03:58.810 --> 00:03:59.860 align:middle line:90%
I'm hooked.

00:03:59.860 --> 00:04:00.970 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Yeah.

00:04:00.970 --> 00:04:03.145 align:middle line:84%
OK, well, now, and you're
writing this longhand.

00:04:03.145 --> 00:04:04.062 align:middle line:90%
>> MCKIBBIN: Longhand.

00:04:04.062 --> 00:04:06.980 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: On a piece of paper
with a pen and your hand--

00:04:06.980 --> 00:04:09.910 align:middle line:84%
you will write hours and hours
a day but your hand doesn't even

00:04:09.910 --> 00:04:10.710 align:middle line:90%
cramp.

00:04:10.710 --> 00:04:12.280 align:middle line:90%
It's not even you writing.

00:04:12.280 --> 00:04:15.400 align:middle line:84%
They were using your hand
to do automatic writing.

00:04:15.400 --> 00:04:17.920 align:middle line:84%
Now, the interesting thing
about what you just brought up,

00:04:17.920 --> 00:04:22.660 align:middle line:84%
in hermetic texts, it does
talk about that process

00:04:22.660 --> 00:04:28.520 align:middle line:84%
of a ray, a soul splitting in
to twin rays of male and female.

00:04:28.520 --> 00:04:30.588 align:middle line:84%
This is part of
hermetic teachings

00:04:30.588 --> 00:04:32.380 align:middle line:84%
and I don't know that
you're aware of that.

00:04:32.380 --> 00:04:33.770 align:middle line:90%
>> MCKIBBIN: Unaware of it.

00:04:33.770 --> 00:04:34.570 align:middle line:90%
Not at all.

00:04:34.570 --> 00:04:35.470 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Yeah.

00:04:35.470 --> 00:04:36.860 align:middle line:90%
So let's continue on.

00:04:36.860 --> 00:04:40.390 align:middle line:84%
So you're being downloaded and
so this story is progressing

00:04:40.390 --> 00:04:42.293 align:middle line:90%
and you have two characters.

00:04:42.293 --> 00:04:43.210 align:middle line:90%
Let's talk about them.

00:04:43.210 --> 00:04:44.260 align:middle line:90%
>> MCKIBBIN: Luke and Grace.

00:04:44.260 --> 00:04:45.060 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Right.

00:04:45.060 --> 00:04:49.120 align:middle line:84%
>> MCKIBBIN: Luke takes a
job at a research institute,

00:04:49.120 --> 00:04:53.440 align:middle line:84%
he thinks it's totally
legitimate, and finds out that,

00:04:53.440 --> 00:04:59.440 align:middle line:84%
in fact, they're doing a lot of
corrupted research that is out

00:04:59.440 --> 00:05:03.970 align:middle line:84%
of alignment with anything
that can be considered ethical.

00:05:03.970 --> 00:05:06.040 align:middle line:90%
And he begins to dig into it.

00:05:06.040 --> 00:05:10.210 align:middle line:84%
To try to discover what
are they doing really

00:05:10.210 --> 00:05:17.050 align:middle line:84%
which is trying to supersede
the power of spirit

00:05:17.050 --> 00:05:22.510 align:middle line:84%
by implanting cells,
implanting technological cells

00:05:22.510 --> 00:05:25.750 align:middle line:84%
or chips into the
brains of people

00:05:25.750 --> 00:05:28.840 align:middle line:84%
who are their subjects
of these experiments.

00:05:28.840 --> 00:05:35.410 align:middle line:84%
They have the ridiculous idea
that technology can be stronger

00:05:35.410 --> 00:05:36.280 align:middle line:90%
than spirit.

00:05:36.280 --> 00:05:38.050 align:middle line:90%
Stronger than the divine.

00:05:38.050 --> 00:05:41.280 align:middle line:84%
And that would give them
control over everything.

00:05:41.280 --> 00:05:44.020 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: What's
interesting about this,

00:05:44.020 --> 00:05:46.720 align:middle line:84%
Ray Kurzweil who many
people would say is kind

00:05:46.720 --> 00:05:50.200 align:middle line:84%
of the godfather of
AI and, probably,

00:05:50.200 --> 00:05:54.730 align:middle line:84%
the primary research center for
AI is MIT in the United States,

00:05:54.730 --> 00:05:55.580 align:middle line:90%
anyway.

00:05:55.580 --> 00:05:57.580 align:middle line:84%
And now what you're
talking about

00:05:57.580 --> 00:06:01.675 align:middle line:84%
are the very things that are
being grappled with in society,

00:06:01.675 --> 00:06:03.740 align:middle line:90%
in that world at large.

00:06:03.740 --> 00:06:07.060 align:middle line:84%
This is the exact subject
that's now on the table.

00:06:07.060 --> 00:06:10.550 align:middle line:84%
Even television shows and
movies are being made about it.

00:06:10.550 --> 00:06:13.700 align:middle line:84%
So you must have been
channeling it and picking it up

00:06:13.700 --> 00:06:16.600 align:middle line:84%
when they were very first
contemplating or working

00:06:16.600 --> 00:06:18.110 align:middle line:90%
on this technology.

00:06:18.110 --> 00:06:21.220 align:middle line:84%
So what you're doing
is giving a forewarning

00:06:21.220 --> 00:06:23.110 align:middle line:90%
to people in these books.

00:06:23.110 --> 00:06:24.660 align:middle line:90%
So continue on what happens.

00:06:24.660 --> 00:06:30.250 align:middle line:84%
>> MCKIBBIN: So he finds out--
he has absolute evidence that

00:06:30.250 --> 00:06:36.640 align:middle line:84%
the experimentation that's going
on is corrupted and takes that

00:06:36.640 --> 00:06:42.130 align:middle line:84%
evidence to the tribunal
which, purportedly, is ethical,

00:06:42.130 --> 00:06:47.620 align:middle line:84%
purportedly has a high level
of integrity and he is thrown

00:06:47.620 --> 00:06:49.430 align:middle line:90%
into prison.

00:06:49.430 --> 00:06:53.810 align:middle line:84%
In the meantime,
Grace has discovered

00:06:53.810 --> 00:06:58.010 align:middle line:84%
that she can commune with
plants and that, in fact, she

00:06:58.010 --> 00:07:00.740 align:middle line:84%
understands the healing
power of plants.

00:07:00.740 --> 00:07:04.160 align:middle line:84%
She creates a
healing center that's

00:07:04.160 --> 00:07:07.940 align:middle line:84%
based on the use
of herbs and also

00:07:07.940 --> 00:07:11.120 align:middle line:84%
personal responsibility
for one's own health

00:07:11.120 --> 00:07:16.310 align:middle line:84%
rather than leading a
profligate decadent life

00:07:16.310 --> 00:07:20.780 align:middle line:84%
and then turning to
technology to change it all.

00:07:20.780 --> 00:07:22.730 align:middle line:90%
To get-- to make you healthy.

00:07:22.730 --> 00:07:25.230 align:middle line:84%
So it's about personal
responsibility,

00:07:25.230 --> 00:07:27.770 align:middle line:90%
it's about health and healing.

00:07:27.770 --> 00:07:30.590 align:middle line:84%
And the healing center
becomes so successful.

00:07:30.590 --> 00:07:37.140 align:middle line:84%
She creates kiosks that sell
healing soup to everyone.

00:07:37.140 --> 00:07:40.550 align:middle line:84%
And in fact, give a lot of it--
the kiosks give a lot of it

00:07:40.550 --> 00:07:42.030 align:middle line:90%
away.

00:07:42.030 --> 00:07:46.090 align:middle line:84%
So Grace is on her
own dynamic course.

00:07:46.090 --> 00:07:49.350 align:middle line:84%
Being the embodiment of
the divine feminine, which

00:07:49.350 --> 00:07:53.020 align:middle line:84%
is all about healing and
creating and nurturing

00:07:53.020 --> 00:07:56.640 align:middle line:84%
and being there
for the community.

00:07:56.640 --> 00:08:00.870 align:middle line:84%
Luke is on his course of
the divine masculine, which

00:08:00.870 --> 00:08:05.070 align:middle line:84%
is uncovering the
lack of integrity

00:08:05.070 --> 00:08:10.525 align:middle line:84%
as the masculine attempts
to control every God.

00:08:10.525 --> 00:08:11.325 align:middle line:90%
Play God.

00:08:11.325 --> 00:08:12.125 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Yeah.

00:08:12.125 --> 00:08:15.520 align:middle line:84%
>> MCKIBBIN: He's in present
and the question then becomes,

00:08:15.520 --> 00:08:16.350 align:middle line:90%
what happens?

00:08:16.350 --> 00:08:19.380 align:middle line:84%
What happens with the
information he has?

00:08:19.380 --> 00:08:22.005 align:middle line:84%
Is it going to be
suppressed completely?

00:08:22.005 --> 00:08:22.805 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Right.

00:08:22.805 --> 00:08:24.660 align:middle line:84%
>> MCKIBBIN: Can he
get out of prison?

00:08:24.660 --> 00:08:25.858 align:middle line:90%
What do they do?

00:08:25.858 --> 00:08:27.900 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: And you're not
going to tell because--

00:08:27.900 --> 00:08:28.192 align:middle line:90%
>> MCKIBBIN: I'm not.

00:08:28.192 --> 00:08:30.550 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: We don't want to--
we don't want to do any--

00:08:30.550 --> 00:08:32.909 align:middle line:84%
we'll have to do a bunch
of spoiler alerts here.

00:08:32.909 --> 00:08:35.370 align:middle line:84%
We're not going to spoil
it for anybody because this

00:08:35.370 --> 00:08:37.590 align:middle line:84%
is a series of four
books that are really

00:08:37.590 --> 00:08:41.010 align:middle line:84%
meant to be read sequentially
because these two

00:08:41.010 --> 00:08:43.960 align:middle line:84%
progress in time as they
continue finding each other.

00:08:43.960 --> 00:08:47.310 align:middle line:84%
So we won't tell what
happens to spoil the plot.

00:08:47.310 --> 00:08:51.000 align:middle line:84%
But the thing is, this
was flowing through you.

00:08:51.000 --> 00:08:52.240 align:middle line:90%
The point of it.

00:08:52.240 --> 00:08:54.760 align:middle line:90%
I want to get to this question.

00:08:54.760 --> 00:09:00.590 align:middle line:84%
After all these books came
through you, did you ask why?

00:09:00.590 --> 00:09:04.170 align:middle line:84%
Why are you following this
information through me

00:09:04.170 --> 00:09:05.490 align:middle line:90%
at this time?

00:09:05.490 --> 00:09:08.035 align:middle line:84%
And I want to know the
answer to that before we go

00:09:08.035 --> 00:09:10.410 align:middle line:84%
and so we have a framework
for the rest of these stories.

00:09:10.410 --> 00:09:12.120 align:middle line:84%
That's just the
beginning of book 1.

00:09:12.120 --> 00:09:16.020 align:middle line:84%
Really doesn't even talk
about the incredible integrity

00:09:16.020 --> 00:09:18.790 align:middle line:84%
and beauty of the union
between these two people

00:09:18.790 --> 00:09:21.030 align:middle line:84%
who any male or female
would say yes, that's

00:09:21.030 --> 00:09:22.320 align:middle line:90%
how I want to do it.

00:09:22.320 --> 00:09:24.480 align:middle line:84%
So why was it
flowing through you?

00:09:24.480 --> 00:09:25.780 align:middle line:90%
>> MCKIBBIN: Great question.

00:09:25.780 --> 00:09:29.250 align:middle line:84%
I ask that because,
again, I was wondering,

00:09:29.250 --> 00:09:32.550 align:middle line:84%
why am I writing
fiction after working

00:09:32.550 --> 00:09:36.660 align:middle line:84%
with presidents after publishing
seven volumes of wisdom

00:09:36.660 --> 00:09:39.480 align:middle line:84%
from the other side
and now fiction.

00:09:39.480 --> 00:09:42.660 align:middle line:84%
The answer was
very clear, we have

00:09:42.660 --> 00:09:50.460 align:middle line:84%
fallen into a pattern of
the disempowered feminine

00:09:50.460 --> 00:09:53.280 align:middle line:84%
and the overly
powerful masculine.

00:09:53.280 --> 00:09:57.220 align:middle line:84%
The dominant masculine,
the patriarchy.

00:09:57.220 --> 00:10:03.210 align:middle line:84%
And the feminine has allowed
itself to become powerless

00:10:03.210 --> 00:10:08.190 align:middle line:84%
in the face of that dominant,
overwhelming patriarchy, which

00:10:08.190 --> 00:10:10.680 align:middle line:90%
has been going on for millennia.

00:10:10.680 --> 00:10:13.260 align:middle line:84%
It's in the collective
consciousness.

00:10:13.260 --> 00:10:17.800 align:middle line:84%
And we may not realize it, but
we're being affected by it.

00:10:17.800 --> 00:10:24.420 align:middle line:84%
So what better way to remind
us that we're all divine,

00:10:24.420 --> 00:10:27.990 align:middle line:84%
we all have the capacity
for divine love.

00:10:27.990 --> 00:10:31.830 align:middle line:84%
To be divine love, to
hold that divine love.

00:10:31.830 --> 00:10:36.930 align:middle line:84%
We all can be in
relationship with another

00:10:36.930 --> 00:10:40.890 align:middle line:84%
that is rooted in that
divinity rather than

00:10:40.890 --> 00:10:46.200 align:middle line:84%
a relationship that exists
because of extreme compromises.

00:10:46.200 --> 00:10:49.470 align:middle line:84%
For the male, what
we call the divine

00:10:49.470 --> 00:10:54.270 align:middle line:84%
masculine is really someone
who's capable of right action.

00:10:54.270 --> 00:10:55.070 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Right.

00:10:55.070 --> 00:10:56.340 align:middle line:90%
>> MCKIBBIN: Right action.

00:10:56.340 --> 00:11:01.090 align:middle line:84%
What we call the divine
feminine is someone who

00:11:01.090 --> 00:11:05.185 align:middle line:90%
stands in her power to create.

00:11:05.185 --> 00:11:09.530 align:middle line:84%
You bring those two
together in love,

00:11:09.530 --> 00:11:14.300 align:middle line:84%
and then we're able to
live in our divinity, which

00:11:14.300 --> 00:11:15.950 align:middle line:90%
is why we're here.

00:11:15.950 --> 00:11:19.280 align:middle line:84%
But we've so walked
away from that.

00:11:19.280 --> 00:11:21.000 align:middle line:90%
We've fallen away from it.

00:11:21.000 --> 00:11:22.820 align:middle line:90%
We've lost touch with it.

00:11:22.820 --> 00:11:26.600 align:middle line:84%
These novels give
readers the opportunity--

00:11:26.600 --> 00:11:29.805 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: It's like a
blueprint for what can be.

00:11:29.805 --> 00:11:30.605 align:middle line:90%
>> MCKIBBIN: Yes.

00:11:30.605 --> 00:11:33.260 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: Yes, and we don't
have any other blueprints.

00:11:33.260 --> 00:11:35.300 align:middle line:84%
I can't think of
another blueprint

00:11:35.300 --> 00:11:39.050 align:middle line:84%
out there that even comes close
to these books in what can be.

00:11:39.050 --> 00:11:43.700 align:middle line:84%
And the interesting thing is, we
see the entertainment industry,

00:11:43.700 --> 00:11:49.430 align:middle line:84%
for example, picking up the
themes of the Ã¼ber warrioress

00:11:49.430 --> 00:11:50.570 align:middle line:90%
woman, right?

00:11:50.570 --> 00:11:53.330 align:middle line:84%
She's going to kick ass even
harder than the guys do.

00:11:53.330 --> 00:11:56.900 align:middle line:84%
She's the lead person now even
in a lot of films, for example,

00:11:56.900 --> 00:11:59.690 align:middle line:84%
and doing things
the way men do it.

00:11:59.690 --> 00:12:02.220 align:middle line:84%
Although maybe even more
brutal, for example.

00:12:02.220 --> 00:12:03.890 align:middle line:84%
So that's supposed
to be empowering

00:12:03.890 --> 00:12:07.640 align:middle line:84%
young women to know that
they can play alongside men.

00:12:07.640 --> 00:12:11.460 align:middle line:84%
But what you just said
that's so important here.

00:12:11.460 --> 00:12:15.270 align:middle line:84%
The ancestral memory
that is in our DNA--

00:12:15.270 --> 00:12:18.300 align:middle line:84%
masculine and feminine,
every time we incarnate

00:12:18.300 --> 00:12:21.120 align:middle line:84%
is affecting us and
in our subconscious,

00:12:21.120 --> 00:12:23.910 align:middle line:84%
that's great subconscious
that we have.

00:12:23.910 --> 00:12:24.870 align:middle line:90%
It's in us.

00:12:24.870 --> 00:12:28.500 align:middle line:84%
And you can be a millennial,
you can be a little Zoomer

00:12:28.500 --> 00:12:30.720 align:middle line:90%
girl who's feeling her power.

00:12:30.720 --> 00:12:33.390 align:middle line:84%
You get with a boy and suddenly
you're just like, oh, well,

00:12:33.390 --> 00:12:34.810 align:middle line:90%
whatever you want to do.

00:12:34.810 --> 00:12:39.360 align:middle line:84%
It's baked into the cake
now because of the millennia

00:12:39.360 --> 00:12:42.840 align:middle line:84%
of living under this
agreed upon or not

00:12:42.840 --> 00:12:45.820 align:middle line:84%
agreed upon situation
between men and women.

00:12:45.820 --> 00:12:47.980 align:middle line:90%
So this does affect us all.

00:12:47.980 --> 00:12:48.780 align:middle line:90%
You're right.

00:12:48.780 --> 00:12:50.700 align:middle line:84%
We may not remember
but it's even

00:12:50.700 --> 00:12:52.652 align:middle line:84%
affecting the
youngest generations

00:12:52.652 --> 00:12:53.610 align:middle line:90%
and they don't know it.

00:12:53.610 --> 00:12:54.930 align:middle line:90%
>> MCKIBBIN: I agree.

00:12:54.930 --> 00:12:58.800 align:middle line:84%
And so these stories
enable us to remember

00:12:58.800 --> 00:13:04.950 align:middle line:84%
who we fundamentally are
and to celebrate who we are.

00:13:04.950 --> 00:13:08.610 align:middle line:84%
The beauty of this relationship
as Luke and Grace go

00:13:08.610 --> 00:13:11.820 align:middle line:84%
through the lifetimes that are
portrayed in the next three

00:13:11.820 --> 00:13:16.830 align:middle line:84%
books is that their love,
of course, is eternal

00:13:16.830 --> 00:13:20.220 align:middle line:90%
and they recognize each other.

00:13:20.220 --> 00:13:22.715 align:middle line:90%
But these aren't fantasies.

00:13:22.715 --> 00:13:26.870 align:middle line:84%
They're living in
difficult circumstances.

00:13:26.870 --> 00:13:29.875 align:middle line:84%
But the quality of their
relationship as equals--

00:13:29.875 --> 00:13:31.250 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: And
the communication.

00:13:31.250 --> 00:13:32.090 align:middle line:90%
>> MCKIBBIN: Yes.

00:13:32.090 --> 00:13:33.390 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: All of it.

00:13:33.390 --> 00:13:35.120 align:middle line:84%
>> MCKIBBIN: Their
decision making.

00:13:35.120 --> 00:13:38.180 align:middle line:84%
Everything about who
they are together

00:13:38.180 --> 00:13:41.900 align:middle line:84%
is an affirmation of
the extraordinariness

00:13:41.900 --> 00:13:45.450 align:middle line:84%
that they are individually
and who they are together.

00:13:45.450 --> 00:13:49.730 align:middle line:84%
And I love that as kind
of a thread running

00:13:49.730 --> 00:13:51.260 align:middle line:90%
through all of the stories.

00:13:51.260 --> 00:13:53.597 align:middle line:84%
They never compromise
their relationship ever.

00:13:53.597 --> 00:13:55.805 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: And they don't
compromise their integrity.

00:13:55.805 --> 00:13:56.510 align:middle line:90%
>> MCKIBBIN: No.

00:13:56.510 --> 00:13:59.010 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: Even if it means
they have to sacrifice something

00:13:59.010 --> 00:14:00.410 align:middle line:90%
in the relationship.

00:14:00.410 --> 00:14:03.980 align:middle line:84%
I mean, it's-- again, it's the
most beautiful template I have

00:14:03.980 --> 00:14:07.760 align:middle line:84%
