So let's talk about
"Love, 24 AD."

00:14:46.055 --> 00:14:51.120 align:middle line:84%
>> MCKIBBIN: Gracila is the
daughter of a woman healer.

00:14:51.120 --> 00:14:54.320 align:middle line:84%
