mother and his father

00:15:14.940 --> 00:15:17.070 align:middle line:90%
were together in Atlantis.

00:15:17.070 --> 00:15:19.260 align:middle line:84%
They've come back
together in order

00:15:19.260 --> 00:15:22.997 align:middle line:84%
to give birth to these two
and then bring them together

00:15:22.997 --> 00:15:23.955 align:middle line:90%
when the time is right.

00:15:23.955 --> 00:15:25.920 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: And this is
in ancient Britannia.

00:15:25.920 --> 00:15:27.060 align:middle line:90%
>> MCKIBBIN: Ancient--

00:15:27.060 --> 00:15:27.860 align:middle line:90%
