00:15:27.860 --> 00:15:29.670 align:middle line:90%
Yes, Britannia.

00:15:29.670 --> 00:15:32.160 align:middle line:90%
She's born in 24 AD.

00:15:32.160 --> 00:15:35.085 align:middle line:90%
So the story starts then.

00:15:35.085 --> 00:15:38.670 align:middle line:84%
They find each other, they,
