00:15:38.670 --> 00:15:44.160 align:middle line:84%
They marry and, simultaneously,
the Roman invasion

00:15:44.160 --> 00:15:45.150 align:middle line:90%
is about to occur.

00:15:45.150 --> 00:15:45.950 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Right.

00:15:45.950 --> 00:15:48.600 align:middle line:84%
>> MCKIBBIN: So just when they
