Roman Legion which has highly

00:16:04.110 --> 00:16:06.420 align:middle line:90%
developed weaponry--

00:16:06.420 --> 00:16:09.570 align:middle line:84%
engineering,
organizational capacity.

00:16:09.570 --> 00:16:15.150 align:middle line:84%
