00:19:40.052 --> 00:19:41.385 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: It was very powerful.

00:19:41.385 --> 00:19:42.185 align:middle line:90%
>> MCKIBBIN: Yeah.

00:19:42.185 --> 00:19:45.360 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: And the thing laced
