Earth's offerings

00:20:23.850 --> 00:20:26.680 align:middle line:84%
combined with human
intelligence and creativity.

00:20:26.680 --> 00:20:29.640 align:middle line:84%
So the beauty and creativity
is very, very alive

00:20:29.640 --> 00:20:32.910 align:middle line:84%
in this book-- coming from both
the masculine and the feminine,

00:20:32.910 --> 00:20:34.140 align:middle line:90%
which I loved.

