00:44:21.870 --> 00:44:24.720 align:middle line:90%
But what they have done for me--

00:44:24.720 --> 00:44:27.750 align:middle line:84%
and this is me being
brutally honest.

00:44:27.750 --> 00:44:30.246 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: OK, let's hear it.

00:44:30.246 --> 00:44:32.430 align:middle line:84%
>> MCKIBBIN: Ever
